cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SD, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with text-based emotion detection using deep neural models. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes sequence-based convolutional neural network models for the task. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with automated emotion detection. 
- cs.SD (Sound) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) are less likely but still possible categories as the paper deals with emotions in speech and dialogue, and the potential applications of the proposed models in human-computer interaction.
